data.description: AWSOME STARTER HOME IN HIGHLY CONVENIENT STICKNEY IL. PROPERTY IS LOCATED JUST A FEW MINUTES FROM I55. THIS HOME IS READY TO MOVE IN. SOME OF THE PROPERTY FETURES ARE, VAULTED CEILINGS IN LIVING ROOM WITH ACCENT WALL AND CEILING, ENGINEER HARDWOOF FLOORS ALL THROUGHOUT THE LIVING ROOM AND BEDROOMS, UPDATED KITCHEN WITH GRANITE COUNTER TOPS  AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, CERAMI TILE IN KITCHEN AND DINING ROOM AREA.  RECENTLY UPDATED BATHROOM WITH SLIDING GLASS DOORS, FULL FINISED BASEMENT WITH AN ADDITIONAL FAMILY ROOM AND ONE MORE ROOM THAT COULD BE A 3RD BR. DEN/OFFICE. CENTRAL HEAT AND AC. VERY NICE BACK YARD WITH A PAVER PATIO AND 2 YEAR OLD  GAZEBO THAT STAYS AND A OVERSISED 2.5 CAR GARAGE.  BY FAR THE BEST DEAL IN THE AREA.
